# STFU

**ShutTheFakeUp**  **is an IDEA implemented currently as Android Application &amp; Website** , to shake the fake news out of our world. Built for **the topic**  **&quot;**** Smart Habitat ****&quot;.**

**MOTTO :**

**Thinking ahead of making**  **&quot;**** things ****&quot;**  **around us smarter, we intend to make**  **&quot;**** people ****&quot;**  **around us smarter.**

As it is said, and we whole heartedly believe – &quot;Correct Information is your Right!&quot;.
Hence we propose our idea.

## IDEA

**Drawing inspiration from the finance world, the concept of Block Chain Technology, which is based on WISDOM OF MAJORITY, along with using the power of Internet through Machine Learning (NLP)**  **–**  **we built a solution to inform people about the AUTHENTICITY of a NEWS.**

**WHAT IS OUR HABITAT?**

My habitat is my home. Your habitat is your home. And our habitat is this world , with immense information flowing around , our habitat is vulnerable, and it becomes our responsibility to make it smart enough. Our perception of habitat isin&#39;t just the things around us, it&#39;s people as well who are to be made smarter.

**WHY NEWS??**

What connects you , a fellow human being , to a person in Kashmir or Kerala or Syria or Israel or anyplace you may think of ? What connects you to your government? What connects you to sports? What connects you to the lavish lifestyle &amp; fashion trends? How do you know your world is changing? Answer these to answer &quot;Why News?&quot;

**WHY UNDER THE TOPIC**  **– SMART HABITAT??**

We know we need to make people smart , we know news is important and makes people take informed and well thought over decisions - which is intact the definition of being smart! Hence why not solve a potential threat to our habitat!?

**HOW THIS MAKES SENSE??**

Will it make sense when all the connections between you and your world through the media and News gets corrupted? Fake news is a growing problem , enough for us to feel a potential threat to the belief people have on our Media. Out of mischief or ill intentions , whatever may be the reasons , we are experiencing an era with exploding fake news at every possible media channel , and the list is topped by our beloved Internet. Internet needs saving. Media Needs saving. We are a step closer , doing our bit.

**IS IT UNIQUE??**

The intentions - No, the Idea - maybe , the implementation - of course!

**AND FEASIBLE??**

If it can be implemented good enough to be demonstrated in 24 hours - we are sure it won&#39;t take much of manpower. Regarding economic feasibility - all our application takes a some space on cloud and some on your phones. Currently we plan to have it open-sourced and if, and when the time comes when it is a big hit - we are sure of finding an economic solution to database storage until then.

**WHEN DOES IT FAIL??**

It fails , when the people make it fail. It wins otherwise, always.
\*Majority Of Wisdom\*.

Eg. if a fake news is very close to being real , issued by renowned authority and accepted my most of us , it&#39;s likely that our application will go on to support the majority.

**ANSWERING THE ABOVE QUESTION!**

However we have included AI model in our application to support / go against the news headline using resources from The Internet.

**        X**  **–** **HUMAN FACTOR (INSPIRED FROM BLOCKCHAIN)**

**        Y**  **–** **MACHINE LEARNING (NATURAL LANGUAGE PROCESSING)**

Using the idea of block chain from the finance industry , we thought of doing something on similar lines.

On our platform (Android Application or Website ) we display Trending News to people , and people vote for or against the news and , using an AI in the backend we provide a confidence score.
